{
  "texts": [
    "With the use of ML, DL and Ensemble Learning techniques in the field of education to predict student performance becoming increasingly popular owing to the accessibility of online learning platforms and datasets, many researchers have reviewed and summarized these investigations.",
    "A systematic review by Hernández-Blanco et al (2019) highlighted the tasks of EDM that have benefited from DL and what needs to be further investigated.",
    "Some of these tasks include student performance prediction, profiling and grouping students, generating recommendations, undesirable student behavior detection, etc.",
    "Moreover, this review categorized and explained both the public and private datasets used for testing and training DL models in EDM tasks.",
    "In addition, the review provided an outline of DL's fundamental ideas, primary structures, and configurations applied to EDM."
  ]
}